{"tid":459060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賭馬心得分享","createTime":"2017-11-05T12:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T13:35:45.000Z","uid":30124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef49ac5c1ba91356e11b3e108172898d2e30db16","tid":459060,"uid":30124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"刀仔鋸大樹篇"},{"pid":"61d6f8f3a7596c32b761ae927cd2fafbb3260375","tid":459060,"uid":29764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"收咀啦"},{"pid":"d0db47b4243e3678357e79f69d5fa6c9d8097bda","tid":459060,"uid":30124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:05:54.000Z","msg":"小弟賭左兩年馬，第一年輸多過贏，今年終於有少少正數，想分享下少少心得<br />\n<br />\n1）賭馬大家都係想贏，如何用合理注碼，贏最大回報，係賭馬前最應該諗既野，譬如頭、尾兩場，自己最鍾意係君達星，魅影揚飛同埋五十五十，平湖之星，剩係賭佢地鴛鴦q,中到都未必回到本，應該要考慮多啲投注方案<br />\n<br />\n2）雷神肯定現時香港公認騎功前列既騎師，但係馬匹實力有時都較次，或者賠率有時偏熱，通常哩個時候就可以博下其他機會馬<br />\n<br />\n3）試閘片段或者睇某啲賽馬節目，有時就會幫到你買到一啲冷馬，做多啲功課，有時會有意想不到收鑊，我自己個人就比較鍾意睇腎仔既節目<br />\n<br />\n4）無人可以估到100%場馬點跑，不過有啲場次啲步速形勢都可以捉到，快步速利後上馬，慢步速利前置馬，如果捉得準確啲，有時真係可以一場翻身<br />\n<br />\n5）賭馬最好真係用玩玩下心態，有時嗰日黑，估中晒頭四隻都無錢收，適當時收收手控制下賭本，黑起上黎都唔會輸到咁金"},{"pid":"8c6dd1774114c9dc3a07868d915b7c5d0cf8a401","tid":459060,"uid":30124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收咀啦</blockquote><br />\n無話要俾咩貼士，純粹想討論下賭馬既心態同角度，唔明有咩問題"},{"pid":"663355ae384834cb39a5b5ea52e7b89463823e9a","tid":459060,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"你講埋D呀媽係女人既野,分乜鳩享呀?谷草出幾場黎過下目先啦"},{"pid":"7b2bbb0a45fe7b2da4bf854cb61f6843837a3d25","tid":459060,"uid":30124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"其實分享下自己點捉冷馬有咩問題呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/213538_b5f15f5616d6864c194a164afb393524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F213538_b5f15f5616d6864c194a164afb393524.jpg&h=828b5ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/213539_ad62c33b1a592bcca840d9784d2b3855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F213539_ad62c33b1a592bcca840d9784d2b3855.jpg&h=f392cdb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/213541_852622202ecc2f5eb424ae3a03269dd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F213541_852622202ecc2f5eb424ae3a03269dd6.jpg&h=19d7025b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/213543_b368bdfe116060058f257323c6c0b766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F213543_b368bdfe116060058f257323c6c0b766.jpg&h=f76f4ce0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}